General.Name: Medibio Ltd
General.Description: Medibio Limited, a health technology company, assists in the detection and screening of mental health conditions in Australia and the United States. The company offers mental well-being solutions for businesses through corporate health product; and develops products for healthcare provider market. The company was formerly known as BioProspect Limited and changed its name to Medibio Limited in November 2014. Medibio Limited was incorporated in 1987 and is based in Mount Lawley, Australia.
